3250","tid":745622,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=h6OxlAPMOdBR2qvgCN%2FjlIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=aaf77c84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯大軍周日出發到美國洛杉磯踢季前熱身賽，不過就未見阿歷斯山齊士的蹤影，英國《鏡報》就分析了箇中原因。<br />\n曼聯將會在美國比賽5場，包括3場國際冠軍盃的賽事，對手分別是皇家馬德里、AC米蘭、利物浦。不過今年1月才「成魔」的翼鋒阿歷斯山齊士（Alexis Sanchez）沒有隨隊赴美。<br />\n英國《鏡報》報道，山齊士周日並沒有隨隊出發，下午更被發現與朋友輕鬆共晉午餐，是因為山神近年來，因為替智利征戰，都未曾放過暑假。<br />\n從2014年世界盃開始，山神每年都要出戰國際賽，2015年、16年踢美洲盃，2017年踢洲際盃，今年由於國家隊未能殺入世界盃決賽周，是他5年以來，首個夏天可以暫時遠離足球。<br />\n曼聯領隊摩連奴為了令山齊士能夠在新球季保持狀態和精神煥發，決定讓他暫時不用到美國。據了解，他上周已開始在卡寧頓訓練場練習，預計將在稍後時間與曼聯大軍會合。"},{"pid":"ad00a43ceb65d994c49caf23b2ecf2d433650ae0","tid":745622,"uid":8883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T02:57:55.000Z","msg":"唔去美國黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729e4134e1ac2e74f896fdf0eaf7c51a1c6e4bb6","tid":745622,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T03:03:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾山形山神"},{"pid":"36e4f5a835e064155ad7d78924e613fe93efcaab","tid":745622,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094cd9f6734817b296d9ecc6f09959052382cd32","tid":745622,"uid":1121,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T03:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com//pgV4856.gif?crop=1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ccenter&amp;resize=650%3A*&amp;output-quality=55\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F%2FpgV4856.gif%3Fcrop%3D1xw%253A1xh%253Bcenter%252Ccenter%26resize%3D650%253A%2A%26output-quality%3D55&h=37c3f752&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d0f